<%= @group.leader.full_name %>,

Your group has absences on <%= @service.printable_date %> that are unaccounted for. Please update the attendance status for them.

<% if @absences.count > 0 %>
	<% @absences.each do |a| %>
		<%= a.person.full_name %> - <%= a.status.designation %>
		<%= a.person.residence.full_address unless a.person.residence.nil? %>
		<%= a.person.residence.phone_number unless a.person.residence.nil? || a.person.residence.phone_number.nil? %>
	<% end %>
<% else %>
	It appears that attendance wasn't taken for this group at all.
<% end %>

http://localhost:3000/attendances/followup
